DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
5482::$$$message_0048_0000_0000$$$::I'm in a fire.[lr]::
5483::$$$message_0048_0000_0001$$$::Houses crumble and people burn.[lr]::
5484::$$$message_0048_0000_0002$$$::No matter where I go, all I see is crimson.[lr]::
5485::$$$message_0048_0000_0003$$$::This is what I saw ten years ago.[lr]::
5486::$$$message_0048_0000_0004$$$::It's a long-forgotten memory of the past.[lr]::
5487::$$$message_0048_0000_0005$$$::I run through the scenery, recreating what happened.::
5488::$$$message_0048_0001_0000$$$::I know it's a nightmare, but there's no way to escape.[lr]::
5489::$$$message_0048_0001_0001$$$::I run and run...I keep running.[lr]::
5490::$$$message_0048_0001_0002$$$::Every time the scene ends with me as a child running out of energy and getting rescued.::
5491::$$$message_0048_0002_0000$$$::[font italic=true]...[font italic=false][lr]::
5492::$$$message_0048_0002_0001$$$::I wake up, feeling...wrong.[lr]::
5493::$$$message_0048_0002_0002$$$::A hand to my forehead tells me I'm sweating, even though it's winter.::
5494::$$$message_0048_0003_0000$$$::"Oh, it's late..."[lr]::
5495::$$$message_0048_0003_0001$$$::The clock reads past six.[lr]::
5496::$$$message_0048_0003_0002$$$::I hear the soft sound of chopping from the kitchen.[lr]::
5497::$$$message_0048_0003_0003$$$::"Sakura's early again."[lr]::
5498::$$$message_0048_0003_0004$$$::Not really the time to be impressed by what an early riser she is.[lr]::
5499::$$$message_0048_0003_0005$$$::I need to hurry up and get ready so I can help her with breakfast.::
5500::$$$message_0048_0004_0000$$$::"Shirou. What are you going to do today? It's Saturday, so do you have work in the afternoon?"[lr]::
5501::$$$message_0048_0004_0001$$$::"No, not today. I might help Issei out. Why do you ask?"[lr]::
5502::$$$message_0048_0004_0002$$$::"Oh, no reason. I was hoping you could swing by the dojo if you had nothing to do, 'cuz I'm kind of in a bind this month."[lr]::
5503::$$$message_0048_0004_0003$$$::"A bind? Why?"::
5504::$$$message_0048_0005_0000$$$::"My bank account's hurting, you see. And it'd be a HUGE help if sooomeone made me lunch for a while."[lr]::
5505::$$$message_0048_0005_0001$$$::"Yeah, not happening. It's your mess; you can afford to miss a meal or two."[lr]::
5506::$$$message_0048_0005_0002$$$::"Hmph! I wasn't expecting anything from you, Shirou. The only person I can count on is Sakura. Right, Sakura?"::
5507::$$$message_0048_0006_0000$$$::"Yes. If you don't mind having what I have, I can make you something."[lr]::
5508::$$$message_0048_0006_0001$$$::"Ah, good, good! Then let's eat lunch together today!"::
5509::$$$message_0048_0007_0000$$$::Breakfast goes smoothly.[lr]::
5510::$$$message_0048_0007_0001$$$::Today's menu includes the typical sides, and the main dish is braised lotus root, konnyaku, and chicken.[lr]::
5511::$$$message_0048_0007_0002$$$::Sakura probably didn't need to make such an elaborate dish for breakfast, but I'm guessing she made extra to pack for lunch.[lr]::
5512::$$$message_0048_0007_0003$$$::Sakura's a member of the kyudou club and Fuji-nee is the club's faculty advisor.[lr]::
5513::$$$message_0048_0007_0004$$$::Nobody would think it was weird for the two of them to have the same lunch.::
5514::$$$message_0048_0008_0000$$$::"Oh by the way, Shirou, you woke up late today. Did something happen?"[lr]::
5515::$$$message_0048_0008_0001$$$::Fuji-nee looks my way as she sips her miso soup.[lr]::
5516::$$$message_0048_0008_0002$$$::As much as she's just kind of out there most of the time, she's pretty sharp about this kind of thing.::
5517::$$$message_0048_0009_0000$$$::"Had a dream about the past and woke up feeling crappy. That's it."[lr]::
5518::$$$message_0048_0009_0001$$$::"Oh, so the usual. Nothing to worry about then."[lr]::
5519::$$$message_0048_0009_0002$$$::It's not an interesting topic for Fuji-nee, so she shifts the conversation in another direction.[lr]::
5520::$$$message_0048_0009_0003$$$::That doesn't bother me one bit.::
5521::$$$message_0048_0010_0000$$$::Ten years ago.[lr]::
5522::$$$message_0048_0010_0001$$$::I used to have nightmares a lot, back when I couldn't shake the memory of that fire.[lr]::
5523::$$$message_0048_0010_0002$$$::But as time went on, those nightmares grew less and less frequent, and I've gotten to the point where the dreams don't bother me anymore.[lr]::
5524::$$$message_0048_0010_0003$$$::I've been told my nightmares were pretty bad back then, though. Fuji-nee was already with us by then, and she's been sensitive about changes in me since. ::
5525::$$$message_0048_0011_0000$$$::"Shirou, are you hungry at all? Your dream this morning hasn't affected you, has it?"[lr]::
5526::$$$message_0048_0011_0001$$$::"Nope. I'm fine, so quit using my dream as an excuse to try stealing my food."[lr]::
5527::$$$message_0048_0011_0002$$$::"Awww. I'm happy to see you turned out to be such a strong boy, but I wish you'd wound up a little more gentle."::
5528::$$$message_0048_0012_0000$$$::"Right back at you. Since I'm basically your younger brother, I kind of wish you'd ended up more delicate and sweet yourself."[lr]::
5529::$$$message_0048_0012_0001$$$::We both huff and turn our heads away from each other.[lr]::
5530::$$$message_0048_0012_0002$$$::Seeing that as a sign that I am fine, Fuji-nee smiles in relief.::
5531::$$$message_0048_0013_0000$$$::"Hmph."[lr]::
5532::$$$message_0048_0013_0001$$$::Honestly, I appreciate her consideration.[lr]::
5533::$$$message_0048_0013_0002$$$::But I know she'll get an ego about it if I say it directly, so I pretend to grunt in protest instead.[lr]::
5534::$$$message_0048_0013_0003$$$::"Hm?"[lr]::
5535::$$$message_0048_0013_0004$$$::Sakura looks puzzled by our interaction.łÝŇ§